{"parse":{"title":"Agaram Foundation","pageid":47157441,"revid":821944415,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Agaram Foundation</b> (<a href=\"/wiki/Tamil_language\" title=\"Tamil language\">Tamil</a>: \u0b85\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bb1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb3\u0bc8) is an educational foundation located in <a href=\"/wiki/Tamil_Nadu\" title=\"Tamil Nadu\">Tamil Nadu</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/India\" title=\"India\">India</a>. This foundation was started on September 25, 2006 by <a href=\"/wiki/Tamil_cinema\" title=\"Tamil cinema\">tamil cinema</a> actor <a href=\"/wiki/Suriya\" title=\"Suriya\">Suriya</a> with a vision of bringing a significant positive change in the socio-economic status of the rural society in Tamil Nadu by offering quality education to the deserving students.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Functions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Functions</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Project_Vidhai\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Project Vidhai</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Mentorship_Program\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Mentorship Program</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Partners\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Partners</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Functions\">Functions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Agaram_Foundation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Functions\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Founder's father, actor <a href=\"/wiki/Sivakumar\" title=\"Sivakumar\">Sivakumar</a> honors the school toppers from rural areas and provides financial assistance to the poor students through his Sivakumar Education Trust from 1979.<sup id=\"cite_ref-deccanchronicle_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-deccanchronicle-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Agaram foundation continues the tradition of providing such educational scholarships to the deserving students<sup id=\"cite_ref-deccanchronicle_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-deccanchronicle-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-The_Hindu2010_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-The_Hindu2010-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Agaram foundation provides these scholarships for higher education to the students from <a href=\"/wiki/Sri_Lanka\" title=\"Sri Lanka\">Sri Lanka</a> as well, who live in <a href=\"/wiki/Refugee_camps\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Refugee camps\">refugee camps</a> located in Tamil Nadu.<sup id=\"cite_ref-The_Hindu2010_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-The_Hindu2010-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> In 2013, this foundation has donated Rs 1,000,000 for the <a href=\"/wiki/Uttarakhand\" title=\"Uttarakhand\">Uttarakhand</a> disaster relief fund.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Project_Vidhai\">Project Vidhai</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Agaram_Foundation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Project Vidhai\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>It has initiated a project named as <i>Vidhai</i> (Seed) to support the college education of underprivileged, meritorious and socio-economically backward  students living in different parts of the Indian state, Tamil Nadu.<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mentorship_Program\">Mentorship Program</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Agaram_Foundation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Mentorship Program\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>It provides a <i>Mentorship Program</i> (named as Vazhikatigal) for school children living in the remotest parts of Tamil Nadu.<sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Partners\">Partners</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Agaram_Foundation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Partners\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Several educational (engineering and medical) institutes and patrons support the foundation to work towards its goals<sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Agaram_Foundation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://agaram.in/\">\"Agaram Foundation - Home Page\"</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">5 July</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Agaram+Foundation+-+Home+Page&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fagaram.in%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAgaram+Foundation\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-deccanchronicle-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-deccanchronicle_2-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-deccanchronicle_2-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.deccanchronicle.com/140706/entertainment-kollywood/article/suriya-announces-new-training-center-underprivileged\">\"Suriya announces new training center for underprivileged (Deccanchronicle- Jul 05, 2015)\"</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">5 July</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Suriya+announces+new+training+center+for+underprivileged+%28Deccanchronicle-+Jul+05%2C+2015%29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2F140706%2Fentertainment-kollywood%2Farticle%2Fsuriya-announces-new-training-center-underprivileged&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAgaram+Foundation\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_n